title: Welcome to Our Village - Please Invade Carefully
description:
5 X 30 Mins

The title of this BBC comedy series (1 x pilot, 4 x further eps) says it all. A group of aliens invade an English village, placing a force field around it. The inhabitants though are supremely unconcerned by the rather urbane aliens' intention of ruling the world and get on with their lives - all except a small band who plan to overthrow the alien invaders.....

All good, undemanding fun.
